              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The isotope identification in the second stage",
                "of the FRS was performed by the Delta-E+",
                "time-of-flight+ magnetic rigidity method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ".The uncertainty is given by authors in data",
                "table without any analysis."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "To derive the cross section, the number of ions",
                "identified was corrected in each case for the",
                "transmission of the FRS, for the data acquisition dead",
                "time and for losses due to nuclear reactions in the",
                "different layers of matter in the beam line. The",
                "latter correction, was found to be about 35% for the",
                "beryllium production target, 20% for the aluminum",
                "reaction target and 7% for the materials at the final",
                "focus."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "status": [
                  "TABLE"
                ],
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": null,
                "reference": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The measurement of the neutron removal",
                "from radioactive secondary beams, which are themselves",
                "produced via projectile fragmentation in a production",
                "target located at the entrance of the FRS, serving as a",
                "neutron-loss spectrometer.",
                "In the first part of the measurement, the complete",
                "spectrometer is tuned to transmit the Fe-52 nuclei",
                "which did not undegro nuclear reactions in the",
                "intermediate target. From the counting rate of these",
                "Fe-52 nuclei and the beam intensity measured before the",
                "primary target, the cross section for the production of",
                "the Fe-52 secondary beam from the Ni-58 primary beam is",
                "determined.",
                "For the second part of the measurement, the setting of",
                "the first dipole stage of the spectrometer is conserved",
                "whereas the second stage is tuned to Fe-51 produced",
                "from Fe-52 in the secondary reaction target.",
                "The projectile energies refer to middle of the target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MISC-COL": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MISC1"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Cross section predicted by the statistical",
                "abrasion-ablation model."
              ]
            }
          ],
